00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:02,080
 if you would understand that he is the way,

901
00:37:02,080 --> 00:37:03,040
 the truth, and the life,

902
00:37:03,040 --> 00:37:06,520
 if you would just make an effort to come towards him,

903
00:37:06,520 --> 00:37:08,200
 you don't have to get it all right,

904
00:37:08,200 --> 00:37:11,480
 but if you would just take a step, he'll meet you.

905
00:37:11,480 --> 00:37:16,480
 He'll sprint towards you, and he will be so glad.

906
00:37:16,480 --> 00:37:17,520
 Not just to forgive,

907
00:37:17,520 --> 00:37:20,840
 but to make you a part of the family again,

908
00:37:20,840 --> 00:37:24,680
 to make you an heir, someone who gets things from him,

909
00:37:24,680 --> 00:37:25,960
 someone who is loved by him,

910
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:29,380
 someone who is protected by him, taken care of by him.

911
00:37:29,380 --> 00:37:34,000
 Guys, I pray this is something that we can understand

912
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:34,840
 and fully get.

913
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:37,440
 I pray that the courage needed

914
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:41,880
 from an understanding of the extreme grace of the Father

915
00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:43,680
 would find its way to you,

916
00:37:43,680 --> 00:37:46,540
 because repentance is a bit of an invitation.

917
00:37:46,540 --> 00:37:50,980
 It's God making it clear that you're welcomed back

918
00:37:50,980 --> 00:37:52,700
 and you're wanted back.

919
00:37:52,700 --> 00:37:54,220
 So I think we all need to keep this in mind.

920
00:37:54,220 --> 00:37:55,560
 You're wanted.

921
00:37:55,560 --> 00:37:56,920
 God wants you in his family.

922
00:37:56,920 --> 00:37:59,260
 If he didn't, he would just forgive you

923
00:37:59,260 --> 00:38:00,540
 and let you on your way,

924
00:38:00,540 --> 00:38:03,060
 but he wants you to be a part of that family.

925
00:38:03,060 --> 00:38:04,880
 He wants you to be under that covering,

926
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:06,160
 under that protection.

927
00:38:06,160 --> 00:38:09,900
 He desires to see you not just forgiven of your sin.

928
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:13,940
 John 3, 16, "For God so hated sin

929
00:38:13,940 --> 00:38:14,780
 "that he came into the world."

930
00:38:14,780 --> 00:38:16,660
 No, for God so loved the world.

931
00:38:16,660 --> 00:38:19,200
 His posture is love towards you.

932
00:38:19,200 --> 00:38:22,520
 He desires to see you flourish, to see you at peace,

933
00:38:22,520 --> 00:38:26,240
 to see you the way that he's intended your life to be.

934
00:38:26,240 --> 00:38:32,500
 And that takes place when we're able to turn from our sins.

