00:40:03,420 --> 00:40:06,460
 He's gonna carry you through.

965
00:40:07,440 --> 00:40:08,720
 He's your strength.

966
00:40:08,720 --> 00:40:10,760
 He is the rock that you build your hope on.

967
00:40:10,760 --> 00:40:12,200
 He is your strong tower.

968
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:15,400
 He is your ever present help in times of need

969
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:18,000
 and in times where you don't realize that you have need.

970
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:23,360
 Even in our stumbles, he will be pleased

971
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,580
 and he will be with us.

972
00:40:24,580 --> 00:40:27,520
 So God, we come to you this morning

973
00:40:27,520 --> 00:40:32,520
 and we recognize and are overwhelmed by your grace,

974
00:40:32,520 --> 00:40:37,160
 by your extreme fervent love,

975
00:40:37,160 --> 00:40:42,160
 by love so extreme that it welcomes in the sinner.

976
00:40:42,160 --> 00:40:45,680
 It welcomes in those of us who are Christians

977
00:40:45,680 --> 00:40:47,120
 and who have made such terrible mistakes

978
00:40:47,120 --> 00:40:49,380
 that we're afraid to come to you.

979
00:40:49,380 --> 00:40:53,040
 It welcomes, it dines with, it reinstates,

980
00:40:53,040 --> 00:40:54,500
 and it restores us.

