00:40:58,080 --> 00:41:01,060
 and so many fears about being judged by God,

983
00:41:01,060 --> 00:41:04,140
 but to the one who would return,

984
00:41:06,060 --> 00:41:10,820
 there is this truth that your love should cast out our fear,

985
00:41:10,820 --> 00:41:14,080
 that your love is enough,

986
00:41:14,080 --> 00:41:17,200
 that the blood of Jesus runs deeper

987
00:41:17,200 --> 00:41:19,640
 than anything your child or children could do.

