00:41:35,020 --> 00:41:37,120
 and you welcome us.

993
00:41:37,120 --> 00:41:39,240
 And no matter what we've done,

994
00:41:39,240 --> 00:41:42,140
 if the thief on the cross could get in at the last minute,

995
00:41:42,140 --> 00:41:44,440
 it doesn't matter what we've done,

996
00:41:44,440 --> 00:41:45,720
 if we would turn to you,

997
00:41:45,720 --> 00:41:51,320
 we will find hope, we will find a father

998
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:53,880
 who isn't waiting to beat us, but who is overjoyed.

999
00:41:53,880 --> 00:41:57,000
 God, for those of us who feel distant,

