00:41:57,000 --> 00:41:58,200
 who feel like we can't talk to you

1001
00:41:58,200 --> 00:42:01,280
 'cause our sin is so bad, I rebuke that lie.

1002
00:42:02,400 --> 00:42:05,420
 Holy Spirit, would you come in and speak your truth?

1003
00:42:05,420 --> 00:42:08,620
 Would you remind that light shines best in darkness,

1004
00:42:08,620 --> 00:42:12,120
 that you came not to be served, but to serve us,

